Pizzelle 2
Version 2 of Pizzelle

1 1/2 c.- sugar
8 oz- melted crisco
1 tbsp- anise seed
1 tbsp- vanilla extract
4 c.- flour
6 eggs
Juice- 1/2 an orange, and half a lemon

Beat eggs and sugar till creamy.
Add melted crisco a little at a time. Then add anise seeds, vanilla, grated rind (orange and lemon), and juices (orange and lemon).
Gradually add flour to make a very light dough (light enough to drop with a spoon).
Preheat iron and grease just before using.